==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
Of Chaldee origin [[בּר]] {{HH|1247}} and [[Ἀββᾶ]] {{GG|5}} (Greek)); 

===Pronunciation===
*{{Polytonic|Βαραββᾶς}} / Barabbas / bar-ab-bas'

===Proper noun===
'''{{Polytonic|Βαραββᾶς}}'''

# son of Abba; Bar-abbas, an Israelite: - [[Barabbas]].

